metadata.title: Tourrorists

Is a diabolical folk power, stew told through swirling mind, Easter psych -rockers, contraband cut ups, illegal pop epics instrumental songs of political sabotage and clever tales about travel terror and more this album is a lit fuse bound to be banned! Discover the inner secrets of an emerging loval cannibalism trade and get powerful information on some of the most exciting terror cells operating both in and outside of the united stated today ! five thousand American died to bring you this album. Forcex. 2006.
